# What is R Markdown?

.big[

- An authoring format that combines markdown syntax  
and R code (R + markdown)

]

--

.big[

- An R Markdown file consists of 3 components...
  - front matter
  - plain text
  - R code

]

--

.big[

- How does it do that?

]

